name: Purgatory™
description: [Purgatory™] is orchestrated with the concept of being trapped in a psychedelic abstract format. For the past 9 months I’ve been trapped in this mental and physical prison like setting. I’m grateful for the training I’ve been receiving, plus finding the love of my life in the strangest of places and wouldn’t trade this for the world. It’s come a time though that I just need out, to be free again! This time portal needs to let me out of the loop again, where I can maneuver with strides in any direction I so desire. I’m personally not any individual to be kept in a box. I have a plethora of plans in the making, love to give, and a life I’ve been waiting to start. As soon as the flood gates are open again, I’m hauling ass and pursuing everything I so desire with determination and persistence....soon.
